  43:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****      (#) Initialize the TIM low level resources by implementing the following functions
  44:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****          depending on the selected feature:
  45:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****            (++) Hall Sensor output : HAL_TIMEx_HallSensor_MspInit()
  46:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c **** 
  47:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****      (#) Initialize the TIM low level resources :
  48:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         (##) Enable the TIM interface clock using __HAL_RCC_TIMx_CLK_ENABLE();
  49:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****         (##) TIM pins configuration
  50:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****             (+++) Enable the clock for the TIM GPIOs using the following function:
  51:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****               __HAL_RCC_GPIOx_CLK_ENABLE();
  52:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****             (+++) Configure these TIM pins in Alternate function mode using HAL_GPIO_Init();
  53:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c **** 
  54:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****      (#) The external Clock can be configured, if needed (the default clock is the
  55:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****          internal clock from the APBx), using the following function:
  56:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****          HAL_TIM_ConfigClockSource, the clock configuration should be done before
  57:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****          any start function.
  58:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c **** 
  59:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****      (#) Configure the TIM in the desired functioning mode using one of the
  60:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****          initialization function of this driver:
  61:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****           (++) HAL_TIMEx_HallSensor_Init() and HAL_TIMEx_ConfigCommutEvent(): to use the
  62:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                Timer Hall Sensor Interface and the commutation event with the corresponding
  63:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                Interrupt and DMA request if needed (Note that One Timer is used to interface
  64:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                with the Hall sensor Interface and another Timer should be used to use
  65:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****                the commutation event).
  66:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c **** 
  67:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****      (#) Activate the TIM peripheral using one of the start functions:
