  73:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim_ex.c ****            (++) Hall Sensor output : HAL_TIMEx_HallSensor_Start(), HAL_TIMEx_HallSensor_Start_DMA()
